Keryx Transfer Syntax (SDR)

    {
    type (notify),
    content
    {
    type (stock-price price-change)
    stock-symbol “HWP”,
    stock-price “$65”,
    exchange-name “NYSE”,
    changed Date:”1997.11.05T08:15-0500”
    },
    system
    {
    source “quotes.nyse.com”,
    publication-id “id://nyse/57”,
    message-id “0f903d1a:67fa:340a95f.0”
    }
    }
